{
  "info": {
    "name": "Marketplace API ‚Äî Payment Webhooks",
    "_postman_id": "marketplace-api-v2-07-webhooks",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "noauth"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url",             "value": "http://localhost:8000", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "XENDIT_WEBHOOK_TOKEN", "value": "",                      "type": "string", "description": "Isi dari .env XENDIT_WEBHOOK_TOKEN" },
    { "key": "midtrans_server_key",  "value": "",                      "type": "string", "description": "Isi dari .env MIDTRANS_SERVER_KEY" },
    { "key": "midtrans_signature",   "value": "",                      "type": "string", "description": "Auto-computed by pre-request script" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "07. Webhooks",
      "description": "Module 7 ‚Äî Webhook endpoints: PUBLIC, no Bearer auth.\n\n**Xendit:** verifikasi via `x-callback-token` header (dibandingkan `XENDIT_WEBHOOK_TOKEN` di .env)\n**Midtrans:** verifikasi via SHA-512 signature di body payload\n\nSemua webhook idempotent ‚Äî jika payment sudah `paid`/`refunded`, event diabaikan.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "‚Äî Xendit ‚Äî",
          "item": [
            {
              "name": "Xendit ‚Äî Invoice Paid",
              "event": [
                {
                  "listen": "test",
                  "script": {
                    "exec": [
                      "pm.test('Webhook returns 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"
                    ],
                    "type": "text/javascript"
                  }
                }
              ],
              "request": {
                "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  { "key": "Accept",          "value": "application/json" },
                  { "key": "Content-Type",    "value": "application/json" },
                  { "key": "x-callback-token","value": "{{XENDIT_WEBHOOK_TOKEN}}", "description": "Dari .env XENDIT_WEBHOOK_TOKEN" }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"id\": \"623fca3f9fea3b00d1c4a7b2\",\n  \"external_id\": \"PAY-ABCDEFGHIJ-5\",\n  \"user_id\": \"your-xendit-user-id\",\n  \"status\": \"PAID\",\n  \"merchant_name\": \"Marketplace Dev\",\n  \"amount\": 390000,\n  \"paid_amount\": 390000,\n  \"paid_at\": \"2026-05-12T10:05:00.000Z\",\n  \"payer_email\": \"buyer@example.com\",\n  \"description\": \"Payment for order ORD-XXXXX\",\n  \"currency\": \"IDR\",\n  \"payment_method\": \"BANK_TRANSFER\",\n  \"bank_code\": \"BCA\",\n  \"payment_channel\": \"BCA\",\n  \"payment_destination\": \"8808123456789\"\n}",
                  "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/webhooks/xendit",
                  "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                  "path": ["api", "webhooks", "xendit"]
                },
                "description": "Xendit Invoice payment berhasil.\n\nDikirim Xendit ke Laravel saat buyer selesai bayar di halaman invoice (metode apapun ‚Äî VA, QRIS, e-wallet, kartu kredit).\n\n**Field penting:**\n- `external_id` ‚Üí harus match `payments.gateway_ref` atau `transactions.external_id`\n- `status: PAID` ‚Üí Laravel set payment ‚Üí `paid`, dispatch `PaymentCaptured`\n- `paid_amount` ‚Üí amount aktual yang dibayar (dalam IDR, bukan cents)\n\n**Cara pakai:**\n1. Ganti `external_id` dengan nilai dari `payment_details.external_id` hasil Initiate Payment\n2. Isi `XENDIT_WEBHOOK_TOKEN` di collection variables\n3. Send ‚Üí cek DB: `payments.status` harus jadi `paid`"
              },
              "response": [
                {
                  "name": "200 OK",
                  "status": "OK",
                  "code": 200,
                  "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
                  "body": "{ \"message\": \"Webhook processed.\" }"
                },
                {
                  "name": "403 Forbidden ‚Äî Invalid Signature",
                  "status": "Forbidden",
                  "code": 403,
                  "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
                  "body": "{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"Invalid webhook signature.\",\n  \"meta\": { \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\" }\n}"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "name": "Xendit ‚Äî Invoice Expired",
              "event": [
                {
                  "listen": "test",
                  "script": {
                    "exec": [
                      "pm.test('Webhook returns 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"
                    ],
                    "type": "text/javascript"
                  }
                }
              ],
              "request": {
                "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  { "key": "Accept",          "value": "application/json" },
                  { "key": "Content-Type",    "value": "application/json" },
                  { "key": "x-callback-token","value": "{{XENDIT_WEBHOOK_TOKEN}}" }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"id\": \"623fca3f9fea3b00d1c4a7b2\",\n  \"external_id\": \"PAY-ABCDEFGHIJ-5\",\n  \"status\": \"EXPIRED\",\n  \"amount\": 390000,\n  \"currency\": \"IDR\",\n  \"description\": \"Payment for order ORD-XXXXX\"\n}",
                  "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/webhooks/xendit",
                  "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                  "path": ["api", "webhooks", "xendit"]
                },
                "description": "Xendit Invoice expired ‚Äî buyer tidak bayar sampai batas waktu (default 24 jam).\n\n**Flow yang terjadi di Laravel:**\n1. `parseWebhookPayload()` mapping `EXPIRED` ‚Üí status `expired`\n2. `PaymentService::markExpired()` dipanggil\n3. `payments.status` ‚Üí `expired`\n4. `transactions.status` ‚Üí `expired`\n5. Event `PaymentFailed` di-dispatch ‚Üí listener `NotifyPaymentFailed` kirim notifikasi ke buyer\n\n**Note:** Order tetap `pending` ‚Äî buyer bisa inisiasi payment baru. Order akan otomatis `cancelled` jika `payment_due_at` terlewat (handled oleh `ExpireUnpaidPayments` job).\n\n**Cara pakai:**\n1. Ganti `external_id` dengan nilai dari `payment_details.external_id`\n2. Send ‚Üí cek DB: `payments.status` harus jadi `expired`"
              },
              "response": [
                {
                  "name": "200 OK",
                  "status": "OK",
                  "code": 200,
                  "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
                  "body": "{ \"message\": \"Webhook processed.\" }"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "‚Äî Midtrans ‚Äî",
          "item": [
            {
              "name": "Midtrans ‚Äî Snap Paid (Settlement)",
              "event": [
                {
                  "listen": "prerequest",
                  "script": {
                    "exec": [
                      "// Auto-compute Midtrans webhook signature",
                      "// Signature = SHA-512(order_id + status_code + gross_amount + server_key)",
                      "const serverKey = pm.collectionVariables.get('midtrans_server_key');",
                      "if (!serverKey) {",
                      "  console.warn('midtrans_server_key not set ‚Äî signature will be invalid');",
                      "  return;",
                      "}",
                      "try {",
                      "  const body = JSON.parse(pm.request.body.raw);",
                      "  const input = body.order_id + body.status_code + body.gross_amount + serverKey;",
                      "  const sig = CryptoJS.SHA512(input).toString();",
                      "  pm.collectionVariables.set('midtrans_signature', sig);",
                      "} catch(e) {",
                      "  console.error('Failed to compute signature:', e);",
                      "}"
                    ],
                    "type": "text/javascript"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "listen": "test",
                  "script": {
                    "exec": [
                      "pm.test('Midtrans webhook returns 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"
                    ],
                    "type": "text/javascript"
                  }
                }
              ],
              "request": {
                "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  { "key": "Accept",       "value": "application/json" },
                  { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"transaction_time\": \"2026-05-12 10:00:00\",\n  \"transaction_status\": \"settlement\",\n  \"transaction_id\": \"txn-abc123\",\n  \"status_message\": \"midtrans payment notification\",\n  \"status_code\": \"200\",\n  \"signature_key\": \"{{midtrans_signature}}\",\n  \"payment_type\": \"bank_transfer\",\n  \"order_id\": \"PAY-ABCDEFGHIJ-8\",\n  \"merchant_id\": \"your-merchant-id\",\n  \"gross_amount\": \"390000.00\",\n  \"fraud_status\": \"accept\",\n  \"currency\": \"IDR\"\n}",
                  "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/webhooks/midtrans",
                  "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                  "path": ["api", "webhooks", "midtrans"]
                },
                "description": "Midtrans Snap payment notification ‚Äî pembayaran berhasil (settlement).\n\n**Signature auto-computed** oleh pre-request script:\n`SHA-512(order_id + status_code + gross_amount + server_key)`\n\n**Pre-condition:**\n1. Isi `midtrans_server_key` di collection variables (dari .env `MIDTRANS_SERVER_KEY`)\n2. Ganti `order_id` dengan `external_id` dari Initiate Payment\n3. Sesuaikan `gross_amount` (format: `\"390000.00\"` ‚Äî IDR tanpa cents)\n\n**transaction_status mappings di Laravel:**\n- `settlement` ‚Üí `paid`\n- `capture` + `fraud_status: accept` ‚Üí `paid`\n- `deny` ‚Üí `failed`\n- `cancel` / `expire` ‚Üí `expired`\n- `pending` ‚Üí no-op (hanya informational)\n\n`order_id` di Midtrans = `external_id` di tabel `transactions`."
              },
              "response": [
                {
                  "name": "200 OK",
                  "status": "OK",
                  "code": 200,
                  "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
                  "body": "{ \"message\": \"Webhook processed.\" }"
                },
                {
                  "name": "403 Forbidden ‚Äî Invalid Signature",
                  "status": "Forbidden",
                  "code": 403,
                  "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
                  "body": "{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"Invalid webhook signature.\",\n  \"meta\": { \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\" }\n}"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "name": "Midtrans ‚Äî Snap Expired",
              "event": [
                {
                  "listen": "prerequest",
                  "script": {
                    "exec": [
                      "// Auto-compute Midtrans webhook signature",
                      "const serverKey = pm.collectionVariables.get('midtrans_server_key');",
                      "if (!serverKey) { return; }",
                      "try {",
                      "  const body = JSON.parse(pm.request.body.raw);",
                      "  const input = body.order_id + body.status_code + body.gross_amount + serverKey;",
                      "  pm.collectionVariables.set('midtrans_signature', CryptoJS.SHA512(input).toString());",
                      "} catch(e) { console.error(e); }"
                    ],
                    "type": "text/javascript"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "listen": "test",
                  "script": {
                    "exec": [
                      "pm.test('Midtrans expire webhook returns 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"
                    ],
                    "type": "text/javascript"
                  }
                }
              ],
              "request": {
                "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  { "key": "Accept",       "value": "application/json" },
                  { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"transaction_time\": \"2026-05-12 10:00:00\",\n  \"transaction_status\": \"expire\",\n  \"transaction_id\": \"txn-abc123\",\n  \"status_message\": \"midtrans payment notification\",\n  \"status_code\": \"407\",\n  \"signature_key\": \"{{midtrans_signature}}\",\n  \"payment_type\": \"bank_transfer\",\n  \"order_id\": \"PAY-ABCDEFGHIJ-8\",\n  \"merchant_id\": \"your-merchant-id\",\n  \"gross_amount\": \"390000.00\",\n  \"currency\": \"IDR\"\n}",
                  "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/webhooks/midtrans",
                  "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                  "path": ["api", "webhooks", "midtrans"]
                },
                "description": "Midtrans Snap expired ‚Äî buyer tidak bayar sampai batas waktu (default 24 jam di Snap).\n\n**Status code untuk expire: `407`** (berbeda dengan settlement `200`)\n\n**Flow yang terjadi di Laravel:**\n1. `parseWebhookPayload()` ‚Üí `transaction_status: expire` ‚Üí mapped ke status `expired`\n2. `PaymentService::markExpired()` dipanggil\n3. `payments.status` ‚Üí `expired`, `transactions.status` ‚Üí `expired`\n4. Event `PaymentFailed` di-dispatch\n\n**Pre-condition:**\n1. Isi `midtrans_server_key` di collection variables\n2. Ganti `order_id` dan `gross_amount` sesuai transaksi\n3. Pre-request script akan auto-compute signature\n\n**Note:** Signature SHA-512 input: `order_id + \"407\" + gross_amount + serverKey`"
              },
              "response": [
                {
                  "name": "200 OK",
                  "status": "OK",
                  "code": 200,
                  "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
                  "body": "{ \"message\": \"Webhook processed.\" }"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "name": "Midtrans ‚Äî Card Capture + Fraud Accept",
              "event": [
                {
                  "listen": "prerequest",
                  "script": {
                    "exec": [
                      "const serverKey = pm.collectionVariables.get('midtrans_server_key');",
                      "if (!serverKey) { return; }",
                      "try {",
                      "  const body = JSON.parse(pm.request.body.raw);",
                      "  const input = body.order_id + body.status_code + body.gross_amount + serverKey;",
                      "  pm.collectionVariables.set('midtrans_signature', CryptoJS.SHA512(input).toString());",
                      "} catch(e) { console.error(e); }"
                    ],
                    "type": "text/javascript"
                  }
                }
              ],
              "request": {
                "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  { "key": "Accept",       "value": "application/json" },
                  { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"transaction_time\": \"2026-05-12 10:00:00\",\n  \"transaction_status\": \"capture\",\n  \"transaction_id\": \"txn-abc124\",\n  \"status_message\": \"midtrans payment notification\",\n  \"status_code\": \"200\",\n  \"signature_key\": \"{{midtrans_signature}}\",\n  \"payment_type\": \"credit_card\",\n  \"order_id\": \"PAY-ABCDEFGHIJ-9\",\n  \"merchant_id\": \"your-merchant-id\",\n  \"gross_amount\": \"390000.00\",\n  \"fraud_status\": \"accept\",\n  \"currency\": \"IDR\",\n  \"masked_card\": \"481111-1114\",\n  \"bank\": \"bca\"\n}",
                  "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/webhooks/midtrans",
                  "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                  "path": ["api", "webhooks", "midtrans"]
                },
                "description": "Midtrans credit card capture ‚Äî `transaction_status: capture` + `fraud_status: accept` ‚Üí Laravel maps ke `paid`.\n\nIni format untuk kartu kredit. Debit/VA/GoPay umumnya langsung `settlement` bukan `capture`."
              },
              "response": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
